{"Id":663992,"Title":"猛虎行","Dynasty":"明","Author":"王廷陈","Context":"上山采樵，道逢猛虎。虎衔樵去，置之林下。樵告虎言，君何不仁。君得一饱，我则殒身。昔非有怨，今何见嗔。虎答樵言，何哉所云。子非我怨，我非子嗔。皇天赋性，有此不仁。樵告虎言，君言虽辩，匪我攸闻。吾闻天地，大德曰生。驺虞不杀，独匪尔伦。虎答樵言，当死小犊，亦何多陈。三日乏食，窜伏荆榛。辛苦见遭，奈何舍君。樵得虎言，仰天大叫，哀声彻云。虫蚁恶死，况乎我人。愿收厉气，敷和布春。尽令猛兽，化为龙麟。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"b5e57fe89c8e7424588bba556ca85057","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6197227,"Sentence":"上山采樵，道逢猛虎。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shǎng shān cǎi qiáo ，dāo féng měng hū ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6197228,"Sentence":"虎衔樵去，置之林下。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hū xián qiáo qù ，zhì zhī lǐn xià ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6197229,"Sentence":"樵告虎言，君何不仁。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qiáo gào hū yán ，jūn hé bú rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6197230,"Sentence":"君得一饱，我则殒身。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jūn dé yī bǎo ，wǒ zé yǔn shēn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6197231,"Sentence":"昔非有怨，今何见嗔。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xī fēi yǒu yuàn ，jīn hé jiàn chēn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6197232,"Sentence":"虎答樵言，何哉所云。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hū dā qiáo yán ，hé zāi suǒ yún ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6197233,"Sentence":"子非我怨，我非子嗔。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zi fēi wǒ yuàn ，wǒ fēi zi chēn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6197234,"Sentence":"皇天赋性，有此不仁。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huáng tiān fù xìng ，yǒu ci bú rén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6197235,"Sentence":"樵告虎言，君言虽辩，匪我攸闻。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qiáo gào hū yán ，jūn yán suī biàn ，fěi wǒ yōu wén ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English"